# Indiana Pacers Game Analysis

This Jupyter Notebook demonstrates the process of analyzing Indiana Pacers' game data using the NBA API. It covers fetching game data, calculating advanced basketball statistics, and visualizing these statistics through quadrant charts. 

## Prerequisites

Ensure you have Python and Jupyter Notebook installed. You can install Jupyter Notebook via pip if you don't have it:

pip install jupyter

You then must install the requirements, which you can do via

pip install -r requirements.txt

After this is done, you can look through the notebook or just run it all at once to see what it does!